    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Now the game is only available in Traditional Chinese</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲簡述</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這不是深坑是一個可以重複遊玩，經營策略棋盤VR遊戲。以台灣深坑地區為靈感，遊玩一次流程大約3分鐘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255280/extras/24f9e196b0a76b8a136c9ab234765ab8.avif?t=1730687628\" width=800 height=460 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲有著風格鮮豔可愛的角色、各類小遊戲參雜著玩法以及隱藏彩蛋，等著玩家來發掘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255280/extras/9b8e862aefa0d6e43687dd4d14004221.avif?t=1730687628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255280/extras_big/9b8e862aefa0d6e43687dd4d14004221.avif?t=1730687628 width=800 height=580 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255280/extras/8fdda2db68704df97e6dab4c1aaf1917.avif?t=1730687628\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255280/extras_big/8fdda2db68704df97e6dab4c1aaf1917.avif?t=1730687628 width=800 height=400 /></span></p>",
